result.name: rain-gauge-rainfall-data
result.notes:
This dataset shows rainfall data from 6 rain gauges located at various locations across the city.

Please note
-----------

*   The siting of the gauges is not to Met Office standards (e.g.. maybe too close to a wall), which may not give an entirely accurate reflection of rainfall. The exact location of these gauges is not released.
*   Measurements are in millilitres.
*   It is recognised that there are inconsistencies in the data in respect of site readings.  This can be for a number of reasons e.g. damaged cable, faulty loggers or damaged GPRS aerial.
